{
  "chapter": 116,
  "chapter_summary": "第116章《奇招挫敌》。寇仲、徐子陵在襄阳家乡楼遭遇铁勒高手长叔谋、花翎子等人。傅君瑜突然现身，欲对寇徐二人出手，却被徐子陵以精妙掌法封死剑路，令傅君瑜骇然以为是弈剑术。寇仲趁机出手攻向长叔谋，以螺旋刀劲碎其铁盾，震慑全场。长叔谋试图拉拢跋锋寒，傅君瑜以江湖规矩制止。商秀洵率飞马牧场众人从容离去，寇徐二人随船离开襄阳。船上，骆方感激徐子陵救命之恩，徐子陵解释武学道理。寇仲用莲香饼讨好商秀洵，最终与商秀洵深谈，揭露婠婠之事竟陵存亡之秘。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为甚么人人都静了下来，究竟发生了甚么事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "text": "君瑜终于来了，我等你足有五天哩！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "text": "竟是铁勒的长叔谋。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "speaker_name": "长叔谋",
      "listener": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "text": "原来是弈剑大师傅老的高足君瑜小姐，长叔谋这厢有礼了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "text": "原来是'白衣金盾'长叔谋兄，君瑜失敬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "text": "瑜姨你好，小侄儿向你请安！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "text": "瑜姨你好，小侄儿向你请安！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁是你们的瑜姨，看剑！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弈剑之术？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "text": "还得请瑜姨指点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "text": "长叔谋看刀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再碎一个，打铁铺又有生意了，嘻！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "speaker_name": "长叔谋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你懂否江湖规矩，这样忽然出手偷袭，算那一门子的好汉？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "text": "当日我和方庄主闲聊时，长叔兄不也是忽然从天而降，出手偷袭吗？那长叔兄算是那门子的好汉，我就是那门子的好汉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "speaker_name": "长叔谋",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "未知在下与跋兄那一战可否暂且押后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": "char_chang_shu_mou",
      "text": "长叔兄无论如何解说，总是输了半招，依江湖规矩，长叔兄与这两人的恩怨亦好该押后。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "傅君瑜",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我并非偏帮你们，只是不想你们死在别人手上罢了，还不给我…",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_jun_yu",
      "text": "瑜姨请保重，我两兄弟对娘的孝心，苍天可作见证。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天由我飞马牧场请客！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_yang",
      "speaker_name": "许扬",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "场主在发你们的脾气，你两个最好想点办法，唉！想不到以二执事的精明，都看走了眼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "防人之心不可无，我去起起那船家和三个船夫的底子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_fang",
      "speaker_name": "骆方",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你们两个谁是那疤面大侠？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_luo_fang",
      "text": "疤面是真的，大侠却是假的，大家一场兄弟，多馀话不用说了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_fang",
      "speaker_name": "骆方",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我的小命可是拜徐兄所救。嘿！你的功夫真厉害，你真懂弈剑术吗？为何那么一掌劈空，都可以迫得那个婆娘后退呢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_luo_fang",
      "text": "道理其实很简单，无论任何招式，都有用老了的时刻，只要能捏准时间，先一步封死对方攻击和运劲的路线，在某一点加以拦截破坏，对方便难以衍生变化，成了缚手缚脚。若再勉力强攻，便等若以己之短，迎敌之强了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_fang",
      "speaker_name": "骆方",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这道理是知易行难，像那高丽女的剑法有若千变万化，看都看不清楚，而就算可看得清楚，亦难撄其凌厉的剑气。故我纵知得道理也没有用。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_luo_fang",
      "text": "知道总比不知道的好。只要循着这目标苦练眼力和功力，终有一天会成功的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "该没有甚么问题，舱尾原来有个小膳房，我们乃糕点师傅，自该弄点花样让场主开心的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那来弄糕点的材料的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "船家有几个吃剩的莲香饼，你明白啦！只要没有毒就行了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "小仲和小陵送点心来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我不饿！不要来烦我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "场主刚才只吃了一小点东西，不若让我把糕饼端进来放好，场主何时想吃，便有上等糕饼可供应景了！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "为何还不走？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "我们确不是有心瞒骗场主，而是…",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那晚杀毛燥的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "场主明察，那个人是小陵。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "真没理由的！我明明试过，却测不出你们体内的真气。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "场主回复正常了。事实上我们用的方法极之简单，只须把真气藏在一个令人意想不到的窍穴内便成。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "真气是循环不休，不断来往于奇经八脉之间，如何可聚存于某一窍穴呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "原是这样的吗？但我们确可办到，婠婠妖女就更是高明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁是婠婠。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "text": "这正是我们必须与场主详谈的原因，因此事至关重要，甚至牵涉到竟陵的存亡。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_shang_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "说罢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 116,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    }
  ],
